    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "NEW!\nSYRACUSE/LaGUARDIA SERVICE\n3 NONSTOPS DAILY\nEMPIRE\nEMPIRE•\nSYSTEM TIMETABLE\nEFFECTIVE\nJANUARY 15, 1979\nEMPIRE\nEMPIRE\nAIRLINES",
      "NOTICE: SCHEDULE CHANGES\nNEW AIR SERVICE —STARTS MARCH 12th\nUTICA/ROME-\nWASHING APO, D.C.\nNONSTOP!\nFROM UTICA/ROME\nFROM WASHINGTON, D.C.\nFLIGHT\nNO.\nFLIGHT\nDEPARTS\nARRIVES\nNO.\nDEPARTS\nARRIVES\n101\n6:20a\n111\n7:40p\n7:40a\n102\n9:29a\n9:00p\n112\n7:59a\n10:00p 11:25p\nWeekdays Only\nSTARTS MARCH 12th\nUTICA-ALBANY SERVICE\nFROM UTICA/ROME.\nFROM ALBANY\nFLIGHT\nFLIGHT\nNO.\nDEPARTS\nARRIVES\nNO.\nDEPARTS\n801\n7:45a\n809\n4:30p\n8:20a\n802\n8:35a\n5:05р\n810\nWeekdays Only\n5:20р\nARRIVES\n9:10a\n5:55p\nFLIGHT\nNO.\n310\n501\n918\n912\nEFFECTIVE MARCH 15th\nFLIGHT TIME CHANGES\nTO THE JANUARY 15 SCHEDULE\nNOW\nFROM\nDEPARTS\nBOS\nUCA\nLGA\nLGA\nUCA\nLGA\nSYR\nUCA\n6:30pm\n7:05am\n3:25pm\n9:00pm\nWAS\n6:25pm\n7:10am\n3:30pm\n9:05pm\nCANCELLED FLIGHTS\nFROM JANUARY 15th SCHEDULE\nUTICA-WHITE PLAINS Flights 701, 702, 709, 710\nUTICA-ALBANY Flights 813, 814\nUTICA-HARTFORD Flights 813, 814\nALBANY-HARTFORD Flights 813, 814\nOneida County's Own Certificated Air Carrier\nEMPIRE AIRLINES\nCall 736-3094 in Utica: 339-3603 in Rome; or any travel agency"
    ],
